<XX>
Companies:-
</XX>
<CO>Applied Distribution Group.
    Bernard Brook Transport (Elland).
</CO>
<XX>
Countries:-
</XX>
<CN>GBZ  United Kingdom, EC.
</CN>
<XX>
Industries:-
